**************** Tips & Tricks:

- Start Linux Mint without GUI
	a) Edit sudo gedit /etc/default/grub and modify line
		GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash"
		to
		GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash text"
	b) Update command: sudo update-grub 
	c) Restart
	d) Start Linux Mint GUI manually with startx
